The Insular Foundation, one of the first corporate foundations in the Philippines, has raised over P2M for our healthcare workers in the past 2 days through InLife employees, financial advisors, policyholders, and their close family & friends. You may send your donations through: ‚Ä¢ BPI - Account Name: Insular Foundation, Account No: 8841-0005-61 ‚Ä¢ Paypal - paypal.me/InsularFoundation and e-mail a screenshot of your confirmed transaction to info.foundation@insular.com.ph for an Official Receipt to be issued. Being tested for the coronavirus and staying in the hospital can have significant financial consequences. Check your InLife policy if you have the I-Heal plan, a Lazada Premium Protect plan, or any individual life insurance plan with a hospitalization benefit (rider) attached to it. If you do, you may claim a daily hospitalization allowance if confinement is due to COVID-19 - based on your policy‚Äôs contract provisions. We want to help you focus on your recovery and relieve your loved ones of any more worry.
